Stampede			KEY:Esuvee ~ Stampede		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Esuvee Race Ability.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:A frightened herd of esuvee flees as a group in a random direction (but always away from the perceived source of danger). They literally run over anything of Large size or smaller that gets in their way, dealing 1d12 points of damage for each five esuvee in the herd (Reflex DC 18 half). The save DC is Strengthbased.																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.1
Swallow Whole		KEY:Esuvee ~ Swallow Whole	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Esuvee Race Ability.Race Ability.SpecialQuality	DESC:An esuvee can try to swallow a grabbed opponent of up to two sizes smaller by making a successful grapple check. The swallowed creature takes 2d8+8 points of bludgeoning damage and 8 points of acid damage per round from the esuvee's gizzard. A swallowed creature can cut its way out by using a light slashing or piercing weapon to deal 25 points of damage to the gizzard (AC 12). Once the creature exits, muscular action closes the hole; another swallowed opponent must cut its own way out. A Huge esuvee's gizzard can hold 2 Medium, 8 Small, 32 Tiny, or 128 Diminutive or smaller opponents.												SOURCEPAGE:p.1
